        </p>
        <a href="/projects/2026-06-rove-to-fl/saturday/">Open Saturday details</a>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Sunday DC / NoVA rove</h3>
        <p>
          C&O Canal as the Sunday-UTC Maryland opener, then LBJ and the
          W8WZ-inspired expanded DC route through WWI. Meadowood and Mason Neck
          remain Sunday context; Petersburg now carries the VA requirement.
        </p>
